{"tid":1992712,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]唔好再開啲咩行動谷行動channel","createTime":"2020-04-28T10:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T11:23:22.000Z","uid":13896,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2c22817d58b1769c5fcccc31663ffb2207484b","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"粗略咁計 呢場運動都過左一年<br />\n班狗都轉左好多唔同既佈局<br />\n令到手足每次都身陷險境<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我地就同舊年612一樣 每一次都大肆宣傳<br />\n希望有大量人流黎協助手足動身做任何野<br />\n問題就係班狗已經知道 <br />\n我地就係要鋪天蓋地去宣傳先有機會集人去做cover<br />\n咁佢地咪一定會事前下更多功夫 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佈防 滲透</span></span><br />\n所有令佢地有更多本錢去捉更多人既方法佢地都會做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">高調有咩好？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">1）和理非可以避開不必要既危險 以免捲入<br />\n2）大膽啲既人可以直程去做cover<br />\n3）聯合多啲手足 更方便行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">低調有咩好？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1）令班狗唔可以及時佈防 變相減低佢地機動性<br />\n2）大大減低滲透機會 行動內容無咁易流出 行動都得心應手<br />\n3）唔洗比我呢啲捉鬼撚懷疑你地咁高調做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4）練大膽啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5）比機會自己多啲去主動熟識行動地點既地形/cctv位置</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講到呢到 大家都知黎緊既行動應該要點做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">我唔會講五一 因為我唔係要個政權妥協 我係要</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立 願榮光歸香港</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc198fffbd833c7a3db913b1b44d53a563dd59","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"自己推"},{"pid":"447f3e85a65cae83b96e23674661908b621f4fcd","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:07:52.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"deacbcd7bd6b20b2b5e9a4553925ca21a25743ac","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"11554c16f675540895fd62c2a89cb82a78b47c94","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"5378a2dc228af92eda98fd1632f6e74c115da011","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"8fcda4e9b81e45b2bfcc64f0d3f209a73f153b26","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"0833841fe7557e45b49a02c1b74262bf54116ca3","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c5c9728abff641588775ba224776f88b31ae61f7","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"1847ba721f19d80e663eb6af9375c579f0c677ad","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"8b3f108a43bd53df1b32a708504587aa680f2178","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"b96733660ed337404c346af6b0914bdcf94540df","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T10:09:43.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"91da4493f3f4f2d54144f0e15fc898e98cc3a81f","tid":1992712,"uid":13896,"like":3